9 April 2010The late Deputy Minister of Health, Dr Paul Molefi Sefularo, will be accorded an official funeral and will be laid to rest at a service to take place on Saturday, 10 April at Medunsa Sports Centre in Ga-Rankuwa. The Deputy President Mr. Kgalema Motlanthe will pay tribute to the late Deputy Health Minister. Members of the media are invited as follows:Date: Saturday, 10 April 2010 Time: 09h00 12h00 Venue: MEDUNSA Sports Centre GarankuwaBoth the memorial service and funeral are open to the public.Enquiries: Themba Maseko 083 645 0810Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)